<title>USA: Omnicare buys Revco long-term care business.</title>
<headline>Omnicare buys Revco long-term care business.</headline>
<dateline>CINCINNATI 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Omnicare Inc said Wednesday that it bought the long-term care pharmacy business of Revco D.S. Inc. The terms were not disclosed.</p>
<p>Omnicare said that the acquisition would increase the number of nursing facility residents it serves to over 264,000.</p>
<p>The transaction also provides Omnicare with the opportunity to offer a broad range of clinically advanced services to a greater number of nursing facilities.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
